list.comment:
Documentation updates and refactoring.
Added license Removed commons.io dependency, tremendously slimming down jar artifact (~300 KB -> ~125KB)

task.summary:
Begin reworking App from Python script
Added through to determining target kernel
Make LoaderInterface an abstract class with constructor
Reworked commands to utilize subcommand functionality. Early offline development, no guarantees for functionality
Reworked commands to utilize subcommand functionality. Early offline development, no guarantees for functionality

Reworked entire application to better enforce encapsulation and modularity. All actual IO operations take place in PROSActions, with Application and Commands package acting as a mediator (Controller) of PROSActions.

Creates an executable now in Maven
Removed Nullable, NotNull annotations

Integrate new Update Site Provider support
- Namespace migration in preparation for flasher support - Port existing update site provider to URLUpdateSiteProvider - Add a Git Update Site Provider (claims 'ssh://', 'git://' schemas and '*.git' URIs) - Bump up version to 0.5.0
